/#
 The specification of whether an option will trigger or expire depending upon whether the spot rate is above or below the barrier rate.
 #/
enum FpML5.reporting.TriggerTypeEnum {
    # The underlyer price must be equal to or less than the Trigger level.
    EqualOrLess 
    # The underlyer price must be equal to or greater than the Trigger level.
    EqualOrGreater 
    # The underlyer price must be equal to the Trigger level.
    Equal 
    # The underlyer price must be less than the Trigger level.
    Less 
    # The underlyer price must be greater than the Trigger level.
    Greater 

}

EqualOrLess.Doc: The underlyer price must be equal to or less than the Trigger level.
EqualOrLess.Name: EqualOrLess

EqualOrGreater.Doc: The underlyer price must be equal to or greater than the Trigger level.
EqualOrGreater.Name: EqualOrGreater

Equal.Doc: The underlyer price must be equal to the Trigger level.
Equal.Name: Equal

Less.Doc: The underlyer price must be less than the Trigger level.
Less.Name: Less

Greater.Doc: The underlyer price must be greater than the Trigger level.
Greater.Name: Greater
